GroupException - Exception in com.compuware.api.topaz.hostcredentials.zos
GroupException is a checked exception thrown when an attempt to connect to a z/OS host fails because the group ID is not recognized, the associated user ID is not valid for the group, or the associated user ID is revoked from the group.
